      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CASHED UP BETH (1) chased the lead early from the inside and boxed on well to finish second, beaten 5 lengths (25.72) at Q Lakeside in a Grade 5 over 457m. Top chance in this line up. EASTLY BLOOM (5) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished in the minors latest when second (20.22) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Expected to be in this for a long way. ZABDON IS BACK (2) showed good early burn and was there until turning but swamped late to finish 8th at this track in a Grade 5. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Cannot be taken lightly. ZABDON SKIPPY (8) scored last time and can measure up again.",
